"```sql\nSELECT t.TagName\nFROM tags t\nJOIN posts p ON t.ExcerptPostId = p.Id\nJOIN users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id\nWHERE u.DisplayName = 'John Salvatier';\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the names of tags used by the user with the display name \"John Salvatier\". It joins the `tags`, `posts`, and `users` tables based on the foreign key relationships and filters the results by the specified display name."